Package com.icx.domain.sql.java2sql

Class Java2SqlHelpers

java.lang.Object
com.icx.common.Common
com.icx.jdbc.SqlDbHelpers
com.icx.domain.sql.java2sql.Java2SqlHelpers
public class Java2SqlHelpers extends com.icx.jdbc.SqlDbHelpers
Helpers for Java2Sql tool.

Class, methods and fields are 'public' only for formal reasons. Java2Sql class can be copied and must be runnable in any application 'domain' package to generate SQL scripts for application's domain classes.
